Name: Total time between First Look Manuscript Submission Confirmation and SW-Reviewer Agreed across all variants containing both activities
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'First Look Manuscript Submission Confirmation' and activity 'SW-Reviewer Agreed'

Name: Minimum time it takes to reach SW-Reviewer Agreed after First Look Manuscript Submission Confirmation in variants that include a revision cycle
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'First Look Manuscript Submission Confirmation' and activity 'SW-Reviewer Agreed'

Name: Average duration of the interval starting with First Look Manuscript Submission Confirmation and ending with SW-Awaiting EIC Decision, specifically in variants where SW-Reviewer Agreed occurs afterward
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'First Look Manuscript Submission Confirmation' and activity 'SW-Awaiting EIC Decision'

Name: Time elapsed from First Look Manuscript Submission Confirmation to SW-Reviewer Agreed compared to the time from Original Manuscript Submission Confirmation to SW-Reviewer Agreed
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'First Look Manuscript Submission Confirmation' and activity 'SW-Reviewer Agreed'

Name: Average waiting time to SW-Reviewer Agreed after First Look Manuscript Submission Confirmation in variants that proceed to RW-EIC Accept
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'First Look Manuscript Submission Confirmation' and activity 'SW-Reviewer Agreed'

Name: Minimum time from First Look Manuscript Submission Confirmation to Manuscript Export Succeeded in variants that later include SW-Reviewer Agreed
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'First Look Manuscript Submission Confirmation' and activity 'Manuscript Export Succeeded'

Name: Cycle time of First Look Manuscript Submission Confirmation measured until the next occurrence of Manuscript Export Succeeded in post-revision phases
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'First Look Manuscript Submission Confirmation' and activity 'Manuscript Export Succeeded'

Name: Time between First Look Manuscript Submission Confirmation and Awaiting Assignment to Batch in variants that contain SW-Reviewer Agreed prior to acceptance
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'First Look Manuscript Submission Confirmation' and activity 'Awaiting Assignment to Batch'

Name: Total resolution time of First Look Manuscript Submission Confirmation when followed by SW–Major Revision due in 1 week versus when followed by SW–Minor Revision due in 1 week
Metric: ERROR: computing metric {'begin': activity == 'First Look Manuscript Submission Confirmation'", 'end': "activity == 'SW–Major Revision due in 1 week' or activity == 'SW–Minor Revision due in 1 week'", 'aggregation': 'total', 'group_by': 'concept:name'}"
